1. The more enemies defeated, the higher the score
2. The more time remaining, the higher the score
Banned Relic: Jetpack

Increase frost damage received by 30%.

0_3.Description:
1. The longer you survive, the higher the score
2. The more HP remaining, the higher the score
3. The more times the death-immune enemies get stunned, the higher the score
Banned Relics: Jetpack, Quantum Cloak
Additional Trait: Elite enemies will enter the revival status when dying and be able to fight again after 15 seconds

FeatureText.FeatureDec: Global Trait: Receive damage equal to 4% of Max HP every second outside the safe zone.
Global Trait: Wanderer's healing received decreases by 90%.
Global Trait: Wanderer's endurance cost increases by 200%.
Global Trait: Gain immunity to freeze when using frost weapons.
Increase physical damage received by 30%.
If Wanderer has stayed in the cold air for 3 seconds, they will be frozen for 3 seconds.

Value.Title: Fragile
Value.Desc: Increase physical damage received by 30%.

Value.Title: Cold Field
Value.Desc: If Wanderer has stayed in the cold air for 3 seconds, they will be frozen for 3 seconds.

0_4.Description:

3. When protection ends, the greater Tata's HP, the higher the score
Banned Relics: Jetpack, Omnium Handcannon
